%% seq_11_notification_center.mmd
%% Scope: list/poll notifications and mutate read state.

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant UI as Browser / Inertia page
    participant C as Notification Controllers
    participant A as Notification Actions
    participant RP as NotificationRepositoryProvider
    participant NR as Notification Repository

    U->>UI: Open notification center
    UI->>C: GET /notifications?page=&limit=&unread_only=
    C->>A: GetUserNotifications.handle(options)
    A->>RP: getNotificationRepository()
    RP-->>A: repository instance
    A->>NR: findByUser(userId, filters)
    A->>NR: getUnreadCount(userId)
    NR-->>A: list + unread count
    A-->>C: paginated payload
    C-->>UI: inertia.render(notifications/index)

    U->>UI: Poll latest notifications
    UI->>C: GET /notifications/latest
    C->>A: GetUserNotifications.handle(page=1)
    A-->>C: latest list + unread count
    C-->>UI: JSON response

    U->>UI: Mark one as read
    UI->>C: POST /notifications/:id/mark-as-read
    C->>A: MarkNotificationAsRead.handle(id)
    A->>NR: update read state
    C-->>UI: { success: true }

    U->>UI: Mark all as read
    UI->>C: POST /notifications/mark-all-as-read
    C->>A: MarkNotificationAsRead.markAllAsRead()
    A->>NR: bulk update by user
    C-->>UI: { success: true }

    U->>UI: Delete read notifications
    UI->>C: DELETE /notifications
    C->>A: DeleteNotification.deleteAllRead()
    A->>NR: bulk delete read items
    C-->>UI: { success: true }
